imdb.plot outline: Arjun, son of the goon businessman is an arrogant man and helps his father. Arohi, from the family of police officers and lawyer. How they ended with falling for each other. How Arohi will react after knowing who Arjun is? How two rival families will react after knowing about their love? Will Arjun change for his love?
imdb.title: Kitani Mohabbat Hai
plot: It's a story about a guy (Arjun) who's in prison from last 2 years and is telling his lawyer his past of being a misogynist and his love story with an aspiring Singer (Arohi). How everything changed and later destroyed. How he ended in the jail.

Arjun, son of the goon businessman is an arrogant man and helps his father. Arohi, from the family of police officers and lawyer. How they ended with falling for each other. How Arohi will react after knowing who Arjun is? How two rival families will react after knowing about their love? Will Arjun change for his love?
